description:
Minecraft Race. In this series, the Hermits are racing each other in Teams of 3 to collect as many Advancements as possible. Each Advancement collected counts as 1 point. 

The Teams will be playing on the same world seed as each other but on different servers. Any players that are killed are out of the competition and can not respawn.
